# Siipet 新增板块开发规范

## 文件清单

新增一个交互板块需要创建/修改以下文件：

| 文件 | 说明 |
|------|------|
| `sections/q-{name}.liquid` | 板块主文件（HTML + CSS + Schema） |
| `frontend/islands/{name}.js` | JavaScript 交互逻辑（Islands 架构） |
| `templates/*.json` | 将板块加入页面模板的 `sections` 和 `order` |

纯展示类板块（无 JS 交互）无需创建 islands 文件。

---

## 一、Section 文件结构

> ⚠️ **强制规范**：所有板块头部（标题 + 描述）**必须**使用 `q-section-header` snippet，**禁止**自行编写标题/描述 HTML 和 CSS。

```liquid
{%- comment -%}
  Section: q-{name}
  功能说明：...
  技术栈：
  - Islands: frontend/islands/{name}.js
  - Snippet: snippets/q-section-header.liquid
  版本：1.0.0
{%- endcomment -%}

<style>
  .section-{{ section.id }} {
    --prefix-bg: {{ section.settings.bg_color }};
    --prefix-padding-top-mobile: {{ section.settings.padding_top_mobile }}px;
    --prefix-padding-bottom-mobile: {{ section.settings.padding_bottom_mobile }}px;
    --prefix-padding-top-desktop: {{ section.settings.padding_top_desktop }}px;
    --prefix-padding-bottom-desktop: {{ section.settings.padding_bottom_desktop }}px;
  }

  .section-{{ section.id }}.q-{name} {
    background: var(--prefix-bg);
    padding-top: var(--prefix-padding-top-mobile, 40px);
    padding-bottom: var(--prefix-padding-bottom-mobile, 40px);
  }

  @media screen and (min-width: 750px) {
    .section-{{ section.id }}.q-{name} {
      padding-top: var(--prefix-padding-top-desktop, 60px);
      padding-bottom: var(--prefix-padding-bottom-desktop, 60px);
    }
  }
</style>

<div class="q-{name} section-{{ section.id }}">
  <div class="page-width">
    {%- render 'q-section-header', section: section -%}
    <{name}-element client:visible>
      <!-- 内容 -->
    </{name}-element>
  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Q-{Name}",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "section",
  "disabled_on": { "groups": ["header", "footer"] },
  "settings": [
    { "type": "header", "content": "板块标题" },
    { "type": "inline_richtext", "id": "header_title", "label": "标题", "default": "Section Title" },
    { "type": "richtext", "id": "header_description", "label": "描述" },
    { "type": "checkbox", "id": "header_center", "label": "居中对齐", "default": false },
    { "type": "color_background", "id": "header_em_color", "label": "em 高亮色", "default": "#FF6B35" },
    { "type": "range", "id": "header_title_size_desktop", "label": "标题字号（桌面端）", "min": 20, "max": 80, "step": 2, "unit": "px", "default": 42 },
    { "type": "range", "id": "header_title_size_mobile", "label": "标题字号（移动端）", "min": 16, "max": 50, "step": 2, "unit": "px", "default": 26 },
    { "type": "range", "id": "header_desc_size_desktop", "label": "描述字号（桌面端）", "min": 10, "max": 30, "step": 1, "unit": "px", "default": 16 },
    { "type": "range", "id": "header_desc_size_mobile", "label": "描述字号（移动端）", "min": 10, "max": 24, "step": 1, "unit": "px", "default": 12 },
    { "type": "range", "id": "header_margin_bottom_desktop", "label": "标题下边距（桌面端）", "min": 0, "max": 120, "step": 4, "unit": "px", "default": 40 },
    { "type": "range", "id": "header_margin_bottom_mobile", "label": "标题下边距（移动端）", "min": 0, "max": 80, "step": 4, "unit": "px", "default": 24 },
    { "type": "header", "content": "板块背景" },
    { "type": "color_background", "id": "bg_color", "label": "背景色", "default": "#FFFFFF" },
    { "type": "header", "content": "上下边距" },
    { "type": "range", "id": "padding_top_mobile", "label": "上边距（移动端）", "min": 0, "max": 120, "step": 4, "unit": "px", "default": 40 },
    { "type": "range", "id": "padding_bottom_mobile", "label": "下边距（移动端）", "min": 0, "max": 120, "step": 4, "unit": "px", "default": 40 },
    { "type": "range", "id": "padding_top_desktop", "label": "上边距（桌面端）", "min": 0, "max": 200, "step": 4, "unit": "px", "default": 60 },
    { "type": "range", "id": "padding_bottom_desktop", "label": "下边距（桌面端）", "min": 0, "max": 200, "step": 4, "unit": "px", "default": 60 }
  ],
  "blocks": [ ... ],
  "presets": [{ "name": "Q-{Name}" }]
}
{% endschema %}
```

